        <item>
            <title>Instagram 全新影片编辑工具，由 AI 驱动明年推出</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/23/ai-video-editing-coming-to-instagram-next-year-using-text-prompts/life-tech/social-network/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ai-video-editing-coming-to-instagram-next-year-using-text-prompts</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/23/ai-video-editing-coming-to-instagram-next-year-using-text-prompts/life-tech/social-network/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[唐美凤]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 23 Dec 2024 03:30:58 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[社交网络]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[instagram]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Meta]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Movie Gen]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1283087</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Instagram 预计将于明年推出全新影片编辑功能，平台负责人 Adam Mosseri 示范了这个工具，功能包括将人物的衣著改变和调整影片背景，亦可以添加动画角色等。这影片编辑工具由人工智能驱动，用户只要输入文字即成。年初 Meta 推出的预览版 Movie Gen 影片编辑和创作工具，示范人工智能如何以用户的以文字指令生成影片。</p><p><span id="more-1283087"></span></p><p>Instagram 母公司 Meta 当时指 Movie Gen 只是研究项目，并没有打算在短期内推出市场。然而，Adam Mosseri 最近展示基于文字指令的人工智能影片编辑功能，并表示计划于明年引入 Instagram，意味著有关技术比预期更成熟。在示范中，影片编辑工具将 Mosseri 的衣服从毛衣变为皮褛，更为他添加了金项链作为配饰，而影片背景则转换为雪地、巴黎铁塔和纽约时代广场等场景。</p><blockquote class="instagram-media" style="background: #FFF; border: 0; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: 0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width: 540px; min-width: 326px; padding: 0; width: calc(100% - 2px);" data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DDwzSoyxRSx/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14"><div style="padding: 16px;"><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; align-items: center;"><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display: block; height: 50px; margin: 0 auto 12px; width: 50px;"></div><div style="padding-top: 8px;"><div style="color: #3897f0; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 550; line-height: 18px;">View this post on Instagram</div></div><div style="padding: 12.5% 0;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; margin-bottom: 14px; align-items: center;"><div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 50%; height: 12.5px; width: 12.5px; transform: translateX(0px) translateY(7px);"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; height: 12.5px; transform: rotate(-45deg) translateX(3px) translateY(1px); width: 12.5px; flex-grow: 0; margin-right: 14px; margin-left: 2px;"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 50%; height: 12.5px; width: 12.5px; transform: translateX(9px) translateY(-18px);"></div></div><div style="margin-left: 8px;"><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 20px; width: 20px;"></div><div style="width: 0; height: 0; border-top: 2px solid transparent; border-left: 6px solid #f4f4f4; border-bottom: 2px solid transparent; transform: translateX(16px) translateY(-4px) rotate(30deg);"></div></div><div style="margin-left: auto;"><div style="width: 0px; border-top: 8px solid #F4F4F4; border-right: 8px solid transparent; transform: translateY(16px);"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; flex-grow: 0; height: 12px; width: 16px; transform: translateY(-4px);"></div><div style="width: 0; height: 0; border-top: 8px solid #F4F4F4; border-left: 8px solid transparent; transform: translateY(-4px) translateX(8px);"></div></div></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 24px;"><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 224px;"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 144px;"></div></div><p style="color: #c9c8cd; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 17px; margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 8px; overflow: hidden; padding: 8px 0 7px; text-align: center; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap;"><a style="color: #c9c8cd; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 17px; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DDwzSoyxRSx/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" target="_blank" rel="noopener">A post shared by Adam Mosseri (@mosseri)</a></p></div></blockquote><p><script async src="//www.instagram.com/embed.js"></script></p><p>Adam Mosseri 同时展示了在影片中加入 3D 动画牛，以及将自己转换为 Animoji 风格角色，全部都是利用文字指令达到，反映 Meta 的人工智能编辑技术具备多样性和灵活性的特质。可惜的是 Mosseri 并没有公布编辑工具的实际推出时间，只提到公司希望能于 2025 年内完成相关开发。</p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://9to5mac.com/2024/12/20/ai-video-editing-coming-to-instagram-next-year-using-text-prompts/">9to5mac</a></p><p>========</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
