        <item>
            <title>NSO 间谍软件入侵手机被判违法，被用作针对记者和维权人士进行攻击</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/22/whatsapp-nso-group-pegasus/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=whatsapp-nso-group-pegasus</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/22/whatsapp-nso-group-pegasus/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蓝骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 22 Dec 2024 15:00:09 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[NSO Group]]>
